cff-version: 1.2.0
message: If you use hapax-velocity-meter in your research or development reporting, please cite both the package and the methodology source.
type: software
title: hapax-velocity-meter
abstract: Measure development velocity from any git history. Reads git log primitives (commits/day, PRs/day, LOC churn/day, author rotation) and emits BibTeX self-citations referencing the Hapax velocity methodology. Single-operator infrastructure-as-argument package, PolyForm Strict 1.0.0 source-available noncommercial.
